article_title: What's Up With Health Insurance Premiums -- Besides Politics?

article_metadata.author: Merrill Matthews

og.description: There are many variables affecting health insurance premiums under Obamacare; many are pushing premiums higher, some are pushing them down. But the sad fact is that Obamacare will force us all to pay more.
